      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this meticulously preserved specimen, presented in showroom condition. Every detail of this vehicle reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market, from its flawless exterior finish to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected and fully documented, this is a premier choice for the discerning driver who refuses to compromise on quality or performance. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a testament to superior engineering and pride of ownership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
